<TITLE> Merkel to make statement on Hypo Real: government source </TITLE>
<TEXT>
 BERLIN, Sun Oct 5, (bdnews24.com/Reuters) - German Chancellor Angela Merkel will make a statement on the financial crisis and the plight of lender Hypo Real Estate on Sunday afternoon, a government source said. Officials from the German government, central bank and financial regulator were meeting on Sunday in an effort to save the bank after a Berlin-brokered deal to rescue it unraveled
